org.js4ms.channels

Packages that use org.js4ms.channels
org.js4ms.channels Provides interfaces and classes for sending, receiving and transforming messages within an application. 
org.js4ms.net.amt Provides interfaces and classes used to implement the Automatic Multicast Tunneling (AMT) protocol. 
org.js4ms.net.amt.gateway Provides interfaces and classes used to implement an Automatic Multicast Tunneling (AMT) gateway. 
org.js4ms.net.udp Provides interfaces and classes used to send and receive UDP datagrams.

Classes in org.js4ms.channels used by org.js4ms.channels
InputChannel
          Interface exposed by all message input channel objects.
InputChannelAdapter
          Abstract base class for all message input channels that transform or filter messages received from an inner message channel.
MessageFilter
          Interface exposed by objects used to filter messages based on some form of selection criteria.
MessageInput
          Interface exposed by objects that can be used to receive a message from a message source.
MessageKeyExtractor
          Interface exposed by objects that extract a key value from a message.
MessageOutput
          Interface exposed by objects that may be used to send a message to a message sink.
MessagePipe
          Interface exposed by objects that accept messages from a message sender source and make those messages available to a message receiver.
MessageTransform
          Interface exposed by objects that transform or modify messages.
OutputChannel
          Interface exposed by all message output channels objects.
OutputChannelAdapter
          Abstract base class for all message output channels that transform or filter messages before sending them to an inner message channel.
